Game     : Record Of Lodoss War
Date     : 2004/07/28
Video    : PAL
Ripped by: DCP
Rip notes: Nothing Was Ripped

Record Of Lodoss War is a 3D RPG where you are brought back to life by a wizard to stop 2 mages bringing an evil lord back too life. Hordes of beast will try to stop your crusade.                                    
                                                      
Craft or find spells and items to aid you in your quest which also has different endings depending how you play the game. Enjoy as the story unfolds and answers are un-covered in this all action RPG.